Lots of value created when devices and applications recognize multicomputing use cases.
Today's multicomputing relies on the user for data marshalling and other system functions; next gen will use user for exec functions only
Multicomputing: using two computing devices simultaneously or near simultaneously. E.g. working on your laptop and emailing on your phone.
